  "description": "This individual is a middle-aged human bartender of compact build, with bronze skin and brown eyes set beneath a heavy brow. Brown hair is kept in a plain, close-cropped style that leaves the hairline clean and practical. The face is broad through the cheekbones with a squared jaw and a broken nose long since set, giving a permanently blunt profile. The hands are thick-fingered and permanently calloused, with old burn marks at the wrists that register decades of work at hot metal and boiling spirits.",
